49 h34 y734 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Divisions have been created. In each of these are capable Division Sabbath school secretaries. Union secretaries </div><div class="t madb x49 h34 y32 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">form a link in the chain of organization in these Divisions, and thus a direct channel of communication is pos-</div><div class="t m492 x49 h34 y678 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sible between headquarters and the Sabbath schools in far-away countries. Each conference in the United States </div><div class="t ma93 x49 h34 y205f ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Canada is also served by a Sabbath school secretary, who deals directly with the General Conference Sabbath </div><div class="t m14ac x49 h34 y14be ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">School Department. This chain does not bind or chafe ; it supports and strengthens. It makes possible unity of </div><div class="t m2f2 x49 h34 y11f9 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">action, similarity of plan, uniformity in method, and a well-defined objective. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
